


# 🎵 Playlist Vibe Builder — Merge Sort 🎵 

## Chosen Problem
Given a playlist of songs with energy scores (0–100), 
sort them from lowest to highest energy so the vibe 
flows naturally. New songs can be added and the 
playlist re-sorted at any time.

## Chosen Algorithm
**Merge Sort** was chosen because:
- It is stable, meaning songs with equal energy scores 
  keep their original order
- It works efficiently even as the playlist grows
- Its "split and merge" steps are easy to visualize 
  clearly for the user

